These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-1::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  accountant, designer, security-guard, chef, pilot, manager, doctor
There are 7 different nationalities: colombian, british, pakistani, polish, italian, japanese, spanish
 1. the chef is on the left of the polish##1
 2. the italian is the chef##1
 3. the doctor is on the right of the manager##1
 4. the pakistani is on the right of the japanese##1
 5. the security-guard is in the middle##1
 6. the colombian is on the far left##1
 7. the pilot is the colombian##1
 8. the accountant is on the right of the japanese##1
 9. the pakistani is on the left of the british##1
10. the polish is on the left of the security-guard##1
11. the doctor is on the right of the british##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3       |    4     |      5      |       6       |      7       |
| Job           | pilot | chef | designer | security-guard | accountant | manager | doctor |
| Nationality   | colombian    | italian   | polish      | japanese | pakistani    | british    | spanish         |

