.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-2::.
There 7 different types of food: blueberry, plum, grapefruit, pomegranate, spinach, pineapple, grapes
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: electronic, ambient, r&b, classical, trance, techno, jazz
 1. the fan of trance is the person eating pomegranate##1
 2. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
 3. the fan of techno is on the far right##1
 4. the person eating plum is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
 5. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the fan of classical##1
 6. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person eating grapes##1
 7. the fan of trance is in the middle##1
 8. the fan of trance is on the right of the person eating spinach##1
 9. the fan of jazz is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1
10. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the fan of electronic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7     |
| Food          | blueberry | plum | spinach | pomegranate | pineapple | grapes | grapefruit |
| Music-Genre   | ambient      | r&b   | classical   | trance      | electronic       | jazz       | techno     |

