.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-3::.
There 7 different types of food: nectarine, pomegranate, orange, peas, watermelon, grapes, avocado
The people have 7 different jobs:  security-guard, manager, police-officer, journalist, architect, doctor, paramedic
 1. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
 2. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the paramedic##1
 3. the manager is on the left of the person eating avocado##1
 4. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
 5. the security-guard is the person eating watermelon##1
 6. the police-officer is on the right of the manager##1
 7. the manager is on the left of the police-officer##1
 8. the manager is on the right of the journalist##1
 9. the person eating grapes is the journalist##1
10. the person eating orange is on the right of the security-guard##1
11. the journalist is in the middle##1
12. the person eating avocado is on the left of the architect##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |     7     |
| Food   | pomegranate | watermelon     | orange  | grapes       | nectarine       | avocado  | peas   |
| Job    | doctor  | security-guard | paramedic | journalist | manager | police-officer | architect |

