.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: hip-hop, techno, dubstep, soul, punk, funk, gospel
There are 7 different nationalities: pakistani, turkish, mexican, russian, british, italian, american
 1. the fan of punk is the turkish##1
 2. the fan of gospel is on the right of the fan of funk##1
 3. the italian is on the right of the mexican##1
 4. the pakistani is on the right of the fan of punk##1
 5. the fan of punk is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
 6. the fan of funk is on the far left##1
 7. the mexican is on the right of the fan of funk##1
 8. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the italian##1
 9. the fan of dubstep is the british##1
10. the british is on the left of the fan of techno##1
11. the american is the fan of techno##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |  5   |     6      |     7     |
| Music-Genre   | funk    | gospel     | soul     | dubstep      | techno | punk      | hip-hop     |
| Nationality   | russian | mexican | italian | british | american | turkish | pakistani |

