.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-5::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: card-games, collecting, rock-climbing, reading, filmmaking, writing, skydiving
7 different pets are kept: cat, pony, rabbit, bird, turtle, hamster, goat
 1. the person who's hobby is collecting is the owner of the goat##1
 2. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 3. the owner of the hamster is in the middle##1
 4. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
 5. the owner of the turtle is the person who's hobby is writing##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
 7. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 8. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 9. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
10. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |      5      |      6       |      7      |
| Hobby   | collecting | rock-climbing | writing     | reading | skydiving | filmmaking | card-games |
| Pet     | goat   | rabbit    | turtle | hamster     | cat         | bird     | pony        |

