.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-6::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: milk, tea, hot-chocolate, mirinda, water, lemonade, cola
The people use 7 different means of transport: roller, boat, car, van, scooter, airplane, train
 1. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person driving the van##1
 2. the person drinking milk is the person driving the roller##1
 3. the person drinking water is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
 4. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
 5. the person driving the train is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
 6. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
 7. the person drinking mirinda is in the middle##1
 8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
 9. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person driving the train##1
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |  3  |    4     |    5    |   6   |      7      |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate | lemonade   | milk | mirinda | cola  | water | tea |
| Transport   | van   | scooter | roller | airplane     | boat | train | car   |

