.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-7::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: western, zombie, fantasy, horror, disaster, romance, superhero
The people use 7 different means of transport: car, scooter, bus, quad-bike, helicopter, tram, taxi
 1. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
 2. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
 3. the person watching superhero movies is the person driving the quad-bike##1
 4. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
 5. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
 6. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
 7. the person driving the car is the person watching fantasy movies##1
 8. the person watching disaster movies is in the middle##1
 9. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
10. the person driving the car is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3   |      4       |     5      |     6     |   7   |
| Movie-Genre   | western  | superhero | horror | disaster | romance     | zombie | fantasy |
| Transport     | tram | quad-bike      | taxi | bus    | helicopter | scooter   | car  |

