 3. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
 4. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
 5. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 6. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 7. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 8. the person watching satire movies is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 9. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
10. the person who's hobby is camping is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |   4    |    5    |     6     |    7     |
| Hobby         | hiking | skydiving   | cooking | camping | dancing | drawing | sudoku  |
| Movie-Genre   | western  | satire | comedy  | horror | animation | spy     | thriller |

